役或10萬元以下罰金\r\n；致重傷者，處3年以下有期徒刑、拘役或30萬元以下罰金。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CHDM/110%2c%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c2038%2c20211230%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CHDM,110,交簡,2038,20211230,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"交簡","JNO":"2038","JDATE":"20211230","JTITLE":"過失傷害"}